{"id":"api/animations/stagger","title":"stagger","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/animations\", \"name\": \"@angular/animations\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/animations/stagger\", \"name\": \"stagger\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/animations\">@angular/animations</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L1272-L1358\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"stagger\">stagger<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/animations/stagger#stagger\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"tf4yezc5he0ooownczk73rd8\">在呼叫 <code><a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>()</code> 中使用可以在每個查詢到的條目開始播放動畫之後插入一個時間間隔。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a></span>(timings: string | number, <a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>: <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a> | <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a>[]): <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationStaggerMetadata</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a50s453j1ko0lr169xuv05dbm\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>timings</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1q6gxub6twzn1umh9eoa19qia\">延遲值。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eu8umecupicei4r1jvi6a9q54\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code><a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a> | <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a>[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"109wrdfussjhou0trnyc8zl8z\">一個或多個動畫步驟。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">回傳值</h6>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6rdp5uc2q5xzkthgskq3aa236\">一個封裝了交錯資料的物件。</p>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/animations/stagger#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"53fpjyhvnu5ksc7lc3h1o6whu\">在下面的例子中，容器元素包含一個由 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 標記的清單。\n該容器包含一個動畫觸發器，用於稍後查詢每個內部條目。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajvo5f50d3fn11sqfz456ubs5\">每當新增條目後，就會執行一個透明度淡入動畫，移除時則淡出。\n無論發生了哪個動畫，都會在每個條目的動畫開始之後，執行交錯器的效果。</p>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;!-- list.component.html --&gt;\n&lt;button (click)=\"toggle()\"&gt;Show / Hide Items&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;hr /&gt;\n&lt;div [@listAnimation]=\"items.length\"&gt;\n  &lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a>=\"let item of items\"&gt;\n    {{ item }}\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eejz12rd9dk9bd7xujyuvb6cr\">下面是元件程式碼：</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/transition\" class=\"code-anchor\">transition</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>} from '@angular/animations';\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  templateUrl: 'list.component.html',\n  animations: [\n    <a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>('listAnimation', [\n    ...\n    ])\n  ]\n})\nclass ListComponent {\n  items = [];\n\n  showItems() {\n    this.items = [0,1,2,3,4];\n  }\n\n  hideItems() {\n    this.items = [];\n  }\n\n  toggle() {\n    this.items.length ? this.hideItems() : this.showItems();\n   }\n }\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5bj6sl078ykmibd9tjorixa5z\">下面是動畫交錯器程式碼：</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>('listAnimation', [\n  <a href=\"api/animations/transition\" class=\"code-anchor\">transition</a>('* =&gt; *', [ // each time the binding value changes\n    <a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>(':leave', [\n      <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>(100, [\n        <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>('0.5s', <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: 0 }))\n      ])\n    ]),\n    <a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>(':enter', [\n      <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: 0 }),\n      <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>(100, [\n        <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>('0.5s', <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: 1 }))\n      ])\n    ])\n  ])\n])\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationMetadataType\n - api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\n - guide/animation-api-summary\n - guide/animations\n - guide/complex-animation-sequences\n - guide/transition-and-triggers\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\n - api/animations/animate\n - api/animations/animation\n - api/animations/query\n - api/animations/stagger#stagger\n - api/animations/stagger#usage-notes\n - api/animations/style\n - api/animations/transition\n - api/animations/trigger\n - api/common/NgFor\n - api/core/Component\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L1272-L1358\n-->"}